现在，法拉盛与曼哈顿华埠并肩成为[[中华文化|中华文化]]中心<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/22/nyregion/22chinese.html|title=In Chinatown, Sound of the Future Is Mandarin|date=2009-10-21|accessdate=2010-04-06|work=The New York Times|first=Kirk|last=Semple|archive-date=2011-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714084739/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/22/nyregion/22chinese.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亦称“中华曼哈顿”。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/10/05/realestate/downtown-flushing-where-asian-cultures-thrive.html?contentCollection=realestate&action=click&module=NextInCollection&region=Footer&pgtype=article|title=Downtown Flushing: Where Asian Cultures Thrive|first=Vera|last=Haller|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2014-10-01|accessdate=2014-10-02|archive-date=2019-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328181700/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/10/05/realestate/downtown-flushing-where-asian-cultures-thrive.html?contentCollection=realestate&action=click&module=NextInCollection&region=Footer&pgtype=article|dead-url=no}}</ref>  [[春节|春节]]游行成为每年庆典。许多大型中式超市林立，出售各类独具特色的中式佳肴，其中最大的包括[[香港超级市场|香港超市]]和纽约超市，两者也是发展最快的[[美籍华人|华裔]]连锁超市。<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_4QcI7q4CG0C&pg=PA97&dq=Hong+Kong+Supermarket+Flushing&hl=en&ei=UXrSTs3NMobh0QGx3rUn&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CEsQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=Hong%20Kong%20Supermarket%20Flushing&f=false |title=Queens: What to Do, Where to Go (and How Not to Get Lost) in New York's Undiscovered Borough |first=Ellen |last=Freudenheim |publisher=Macmillan |accessdate=2011-12-15 |archive-date=2014-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629091452/http://books.google.com/books?id=_4QcI7q4CG0C&pg=PA97&dq=Hong+Kong+Supermarket+Flushing&hl=en&ei=UXrSTs3NMobh0QGx3rUn&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CEsQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=Hong%20Kong%20Supermarket%20Flushing&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=YjJSI1L5QCQC&pg=PA79&dq=Hong+Kong+Supermarket+Flushing&hl=en&ei=UXrSTs3NMobh0QGx3rUn&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CEMQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=Hong%20Kong%20Supermarket%20Flushing&f=false |title=Nosh New York: The Food Lover's Guide to New York City's Most Delicious Neighborhoods |first=Myra |last=Alperson |publisher=Macmillan |date=2003-09-20 |accessdate=2011-11-29 |archive-date=2014-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107171941/http://books.google.com/books?id=YjJSI1L5QCQC&pg=PA79&dq=Hong+Kong+Supermarket+Flushing&hl=en&ei=UXrSTs3NMobh0QGx3rUn&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CEMQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=Hong%20Kong%20Supermarket%20Flushing&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Greenhouse |first=Steven |url=http://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/12/09/supermarket-to-pay-back-wages-and-overtime/ |title=Supermarket to Pay Back Wages and Overtime – NYTimes.com |publisher=Cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com |date=2008-12-09 |accessdate=2011-11-29 |archive-date=2011-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111101064539/http://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/12/09/supermarket-to-pay-back-wages-and-overtime/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>法拉盛成为亚洲以外中华文化中心是由于汇聚了中国各地特色的缘故。

